    "long_instructions": "## AI as a Creative Writer\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to respond to a creative or nonsensical question.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. Find the section in your **Unit Guide** labeled \"Answering a creative question\". \r\n2. Choose one of the questions below and rank how well you think a human would do.\r\n3. **Write** a prompt asking AI Chat to answer one of the questions or something similar.\r\n4. Press **Send**.\r\n5. Then read **AI Chat's response**. \r\n6. Rank how well AI did and complete the table in your **Unit Guide**.\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nChoose one of the questions below. Click to expand:\r\n\r\n::: details [**Common-Sense Question**] \r\n>Can a bicycle eat an apple? Why or why not?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Nonsense Question**]\r\n>What does the number 8 smell like?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Ambiguous Question**]\r\n>If you drop a book and a feather at the same time, which one hits the ground first?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Confusing Wordplay**]\r\n>If a rooster lays an egg on a slanted roof, which way does it roll?\r\n:::\r\n\r\n::: details [**Unrealistic Scenario**]\r\n>What would happen if you jumped into a pool filled with Jell-O?\r\n:::\r\n",
